{"tid":1488531,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中聯辦旗下網媒批李嘉誠「矮身過牆窿」，讚吳光正「風格強悍」","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:12:23.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"245634fa6a74af2308db316be9f8a184052ded29","tid":1488531,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠個人名義在香港相當一部份報紙刊登全版的「立場式」廣告，以他的老年階段的思想、行為，尤其是今次关係香港前途生死存亡的關鍵時刻，唯一一次对「香港情」的表現和态度，是意图扮演一個温和带有苦口婆心的形像。<br />\n<br />\n他的八十六歲政治智慧原來是如此，看來是他悠悠歲月留給全體港人最後一個範本。香港人是不是都認同他在事件中的政治表現和處理方式，港人自講。不妨拭目以待罷。<br />\n<br />\n肯定他有做咗事，但在我眼中，形容他今次處理，在政治智慧上做事有「矮身過牆窿，左顧右盼」，企图想两面討好之嫌，只會落得一個豬八怪照鏡，两面不是人的下場。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠作為老人階段，對國家的态度，發生如此微妙變化，令人很不解？但似乎冥冥中已有安排。他的身價按福布斯亿萬富豪排行榜估計329億美元，有相當一部份放在海外，尤其相當部份放在英國。未知是不是這種資産安排附带作用，令人産生感覺：李嘉誠既熟悉又陌生。<br />\n<br />\n八月十七日他在香港多份報紙，出錢刊登的全版廣告，必將成為未來大學政治、新聞学明辨黑白是非的一份典型教材。<br />\n<br />\n回頭再看吴光正本周一(12/8 )的文章，立埸鮮明、態度明确、一針見血，似足他在商事的那種强悍風格。一剛一柔，两位名人在事件現階段的各自政治智慧、處理手法、方式試作比較，再猜想李嘉誠的二則廣告含義，我較欣賞吴的文章，不似李的「黄台之瓜」，有過份滑頭之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n以他的年紀和地位，如此造作，何必呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ftopic%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F08%2F17%2F010124101.shtml&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NALXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3c0ccec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ftopic%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F08%2F17%2F010124101.shtml&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NALXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3c0ccec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ftopic%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F08%2F17%2F010124101.shtml&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NALXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3c0ccec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/08/17/010124101.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"cbd7ec7d19158689a2a1709de7b232ed1405ad4c","tid":1488531,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思 麻煩大家幫手投票定個死線<br />\n大家既訴求唔可以不了了之</span></span><br />\n死線投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488382</a>"},{"pid":"161d33d43651d4a81f8883348c382fdb7e6d9cd6","tid":1488531,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"做得好 最好就係咁推誠哥過黎我地呢邊"},{"pid":"64ef06df6bba95f75bb7fa91e2acb6e9f7175b24","tid":1488531,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"知道邊個係偽政府港督啦宜家？"},{"pid":"abfef71295854982ca452f2471a5ba4f0fba1dab","tid":1488531,"uid":256296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2yr3PB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2yr3PB.jpg&h=a0354231&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnhHB9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnhHB9C.jpg&h=b5a1c199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSSgGBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSSgGBQ.jpg&h=ad3646fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svC08gQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvC08gQ.jpg&h=6c9c72fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87c67b3678b176bcbba91a937151a5ecd454fff3","tid":1488531,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:12:23.000Z","msg":"專登出篇文去講誠哥，洗唔洗咁怨婦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連吳光正呢d二打六都要吹奏，真係好恨阿誠哥撤資<im